    ğŸ”¹ `--abi-version <number>` --> ğŸ”¢ Change the ABI version.
    ğŸ”¹ `--output-file <file>` --> ğŸ“¤ Write the changes to a new file instead of modifying the original.
    ğŸ”¹ `--print-version` --> â„¹ï¸ Print the version of `elfedit`.
    ğŸ”¹ `--help` --> â“ Display help information for the `elfedit` command.

ğŸ›  **Examples:**

    $ elfedit --architecture x86_64 myprogram

